{"tid":2440999,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"檢測五呈陰性 院舍職員抽痰揭中招","createTime":"2021-03-10T11:01:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T11:01:30.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0262e2e47215c83cc9e40057c3f4883721958284","tid":2440999,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T11:01:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210310/HVJKN5GT5RB37GHTY47NLZUJZM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210310%2FHVJKN5GT5RB37GHTY47NLZUJZM%2F&d=QSug7dhZHD7voFbR5lwplagSrXaipXgDiqSA7FZ3Rlo%3D&h=acf0f2a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210310%2FHVJKN5GT5RB37GHTY47NLZUJZM%2F&h=18a3db77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210310/HVJKN5GT5RB37GHTY47NLZUJZM/</a><br />\n<br />\n檢測五呈陰性 院舍職員抽痰揭中招<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/RORwnugi0ZI5OAGn9NwqUVStw4o=/510x286/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QK3YMNMIGNAFHH5CK25RQVQU64.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FRORwnugi0ZI5OAGn9NwqUVStw4o%3D%2F510x286%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQK3YMNMIGNAFHH5CK25RQVQU64.jpg&h=90d72308&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■樂道居殘疾院舍近70人撤離，一名男子昨由擔架床送院。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】觀塘心理衞生會樂道居殘疾人士院舍一名活動助理初步確診，患者上月22日發病，先後五次檢測均呈陰性，直至昨日抽取支氣管分泌物始對病毒呈陽性，並已有抗體，共約70名院友及員工須送往檢疫。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：指死亡率高過內地 不符數據 「聶」造事實 拒煞停長者接種<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n逾70院友員工入營<br />\n<br />\n患者為一名26歲男子，居於坑口厚德邨德安樓，於觀塘功樂道香港心理衞生會樂道居工作，2月22日發燒，23日、3月1日曾進行深喉唾液檢測，結果呈陰性。惟患者病情未見好轉，3月3日經急症室入住聯合醫院，院方再於同日、5日及7日三次為病人檢測，結果同為陰性。<br />\n<br />\n到昨日，院方抽取患者的支氣管分泌物化驗，結果呈陽性，血液樣本抗體測試亦呈陽性。該院11名病人列為密切接觸者須隔離檢疫，他們檢測結果為陰性，病房環境樣本測試亦呈陰性。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：潛伏期與友午膳 毒襲鄰近餐枱  名潮患者疑傳海饌三食客<br />\n<br />\n防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n昨晚約7時10分，兩架。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n對於有患者五次檢測仍驗不到病毒，呼吸系統專科醫生梁子超解釋，患者的病毒未必集中於上呼吸道，深喉唾液樣本未必化驗到，當患者感染病毒一段時間，出現肺炎病徵後，病毒便會於下呼吸道呈現。<br />\n<br />\n另有兩宗源頭不明的初步確診個案，已被列強檢大廈的葵涌華景山路海峰花園1座再有住客染疫，患者是一名58歲男子，於深水埗區醫局街怡高工業中心工作，曾與友人在華景山莊打網球，未有戴口罩。此外，病人曾光顧不少藍店，包括葵芳敏華冰室、長沙灣意樂餐廳、翠華、百份百餐廳及旺角新世紀廣場美心千両，亦曾去過頤東酒家。<br />\n<br />\n另一個案是西營盤。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/RORwnugi0ZI5OAGn9NwqUVStw4o=/510x286/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QK3YMNMIGNAFHH5CK25RQVQU64.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FRORwnugi0ZI5OAGn9NwqUVStw4o%3D%2F510x286%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQK3YMNMIGNAFHH5CK25RQVQU64.jpg&h=90d72308&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/PY_GAC81JD2AiReqvNFyUunRewo=/426x600/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BJXLVWRMGRHM7N2PCZGD4TVFMI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FPY_GAC81JD2AiReqvNFyUunRewo%3D%2F426x600%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBJXLVWRMGRHM7N2PCZGD4TVFMI.jpg&h=da5d5e4e&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}